# Frontend Rules (n8n as UI)

## Core Principle
This project has NO traditional frontend framework. The user interface IS n8n's Chat Trigger.
No Next.js, no React, no Vue, no Tailwind, no build step.

## Interaction Model
- **Daily Standup**: n8n Chat Trigger (single room, all participants)
- **Sprint Planning**: n8n Chat Trigger (Scrum Master only)
- **User Story Generation**: n8n Chat Trigger (Scrum Master only) — STRETCH
- **Blocker Capture**: GitHub webhook or direct n8n webhook form

## If a Dashboard Is Added (STRETCH)
If time permits building a status dashboard:
- Serve a single HTML page from FastAPI (no build step)
- Use vanilla JS or htmx — no React/Next.js
- No separate frontend deployment
- No npm, no bundler, no Tailwind

## No Alternative UI
Do NOT suggest or build Slack bots, Discord bots, Telegram bots, or any other chat platform integration.
The n8n Chat Trigger is the only UI for the MVP.
